00:38:19,913 --> 00:38:22,214
你根本没想伤害他 你只是想...
So you didn't want to hurt him, you just wanted to...

680
00:38:22,248 --> 00:38:24,249
把他逼疯
make him crazy?

681
00:38:26,219 --> 00:38:27,386
你知道什么真正的疯么
You wanna know what's crazy?

682
00:38:27,420 --> 00:38:29,388
我父母过世的时候
When my parents died,

683
00:38:29,422 --> 00:38:31,190
他们把房子留给了艾德 
they left Ed the house, 

684
00:38:31,191 --> 00:38:32,958
只留给我他们的毕生积蓄
and me, their life savings

685
00:38:32,992 --> 00:38:35,093
九千美元
of $9000.

686
00:38:38,364 --> 00:38:40,699
这怎么可能公平
How is that fair?

687
00:38:44,003 --> 00:38:46,638
有什么收获
What did you get?

688
00:38:46,672 --> 00:38:49,406
那所房子 而且他要支付维修费用
The house. And he is going to pay damages.

689
00:38:49,440 --> 00:38:52,042
- 不错 多谢 - 客气
- Good. Thank you.- Pleasure.

690
00:38:52,076 --> 00:38:55,679
嗨 艾登 关于昨晚...
Hey, Aidan? About last night...

691
00:38:55,714 --> 00:38:58,081
哦 我早早就上床了
Yeah, I went to bed early.

692
00:38:58,116 --> 00:39:00,083
读了本书 是个很平静的夜晚
Read a book. It was a quiet night.

693
00:39:00,118 --> 00:39:02,085
你呢
How about you?

694
00:39:02,120 --> 00:39:05,087
和你差不多 呆在家里
Pretty much the same. Just stayed in.

695
00:39:05,122 --> 00:39:07,757
你应该出去走走 享受生活
You should get out. Have a life.

696
00:39:07,791 --> 00:39:09,792
抽空吧
One of these days.

697
00:39:13,363 --> 00:39:15,331
艾德 你生气没关系的
Ed, it's OK to be angry.

698
00:39:15,365 --> 00:39:18,601
别开玩笑了 我是很生气... 夏洛克
No kidding, I'm angry... Sherlock.

699
00:39:18,636 --> 00:39:22,337
我连自己亲弟弟都不能信了 还能信谁呢
You can't trust your own brother, who can you trust?

700
00:39:22,371 --> 00:39:25,741
信你自己 艾德 马库斯想把你逼疯
Yourself, Ed. Marcus tried to push you

701
00:39:25,775 --> 00:39:28,043
可别让他得逞
over the edge into a breakdown. Don't let him win.

702
00:39:28,077 --> 00:39:31,112
他已经把我逼疯了 我都住院了 不是吗
He already did! I'm in a hospital, aren't I?

703
00:39:31,147 --> 00:39:35,383
已经准备好开庭了 基诺斯基先生
The board is ready for us, Mr. Janoski.

704
00:39:35,418 --> 00:39:38,019
律师 你们可能会把我关在这儿一辈子
Lawyers. You'll probably get me locked up in here

705
00:39:38,053 --> 00:39:41,722
- 我不去 - 再给我们几分钟时间
- for years. I'm not going! - Just give us a minute.

706
00:39:43,959 --> 00:39:47,327
艾德 你要去参加那个听证会
Ed, you're going to go into that hearing

707
00:39:47,362 --> 00:39:49,764
告诉他们那房子是属于你的
and show them that you belong in your own house.

708
00:39:49,798 --> 00:39:53,033
没人能帮你做这件事
No one can do that for you.

709
00:39:53,067 --> 00:39:56,036
我知道你很清楚自己的经济状况
I know that you understand your finances perfectly well.

710
00:39:56,070 --> 00:39:58,038
你的确可能需要些小小的帮助
You might need a little bit of help,

711
00:39:58,072 --> 00:40:02,442
但是你不必呆在医院里了
but you don't need to be in a hospital.

712
00:40:02,476 --> 00:40:04,410
诺尔玛不会想让你呆在这里的
Norma wouldn't want you here.

713
00:40:06,280 --> 00:40:08,313
你能做到的艾德
You can do this, Ed.

714
00:40:08,347 --> 00:40:11,584
别对我说教
Don't patronize me.

715
00:40:11,618 --> 00:40:14,920
你想寻求优越感么 替别人换便盆去吧
You want to feel superior, go change somebody's bedpan.

716
00:40:14,955 --> 00:40:16,956
我能照顾好我自己
I can take care of myself.

717
00:40:28,000 --> 00:40:29,968
准备好了吗
You ready?

718
00:40:30,002 --> 00:40:34,739
这让我想起了我和诺尔玛结婚那天
It reminds me of the day Norma and I got married.

719
00:40:34,773 --> 00:40:36,741
时机刚好
Perfect timing.

720
00:40:36,775 --> 00:40:38,743
希望我没打扰到你们
I hope I'm not interrupting anything.

721
00:40:38,777 --> 00:40:41,678
你到底想要什么 他这是擅闯民宅
What the hell do you want? He's trespassing.

722
00:40:41,713 --> 00:40:43,647
特伦布莱先生有话说
Mr. Tremblay has something to say.

723
00:40:43,681 --> 00:40:46,583
我谨代表我自己和我的工作人员
On behalf of myself and my crew,

724
00:40:46,618 --> 00:40:49,452
表达我诚挚的歉意
I would like to offer a sincere apology

725
00:40:49,487 --> 00:40:52,489
如果我们的施工对你产生了任何不便
for any distress that our construction may have caused you.

726
00:40:52,523 --> 00:40:54,491
我希望
And I hope that that

727
00:40:54,525 --> 00:40:57,693
这可以弥补您的损失
is enough to cover the damages to your house.

728
00:40:57,728 --> 00:41:00,029
啊
Ah!

729
00:41:00,063 --> 00:41:02,397
你不必如此慷慨
You didn't have to be that generous.

730
00:41:02,432 --> 00:41:06,335
是的 他是 还有...
Yeah, he did. And...

731
00:41:06,369 --> 00:41:09,571
还有...
And...

732
00:41:16,245 --> 00:41:18,947
我不知道说什么了
I don't know what to say.

733
00:41:18,981 --> 00:41:20,982
诺尔玛是个很会说话的人
Norma was the one that was good with words.

734
00:41:21,017 --> 00:41:24,919
- 那她会怎么说 - 如果你渴望什么
- What would she have said? - If you want something in life,

735
00:41:24,954 --> 00:41:27,155
就去努力争取
you got to fight for it.

736
00:41:27,189 --> 00:41:30,457
杰西卡和戴夫要搬到柏林顿去了
Jessica and Dave are moving to Burlington.

737
00:41:30,491 --> 00:41:34,327
法官允许他们在新小区里做社区服务
Judge is allowing them to do community service in their new 'hood.

738
00:41:36,731 --> 00:41:40,000
这就像感恩节 圣诞节 和我的生日一样
It's like Thanksgiving, Christmas, and my birthday...

739
00:41:42,003 --> 00:41:45,104
哈 所有节日合在一起了
Ha! All rolled into one.

740
00:41:51,578 --> 00:41:53,546
希望没人指望我
I hope none of you were expecting me

741
00:41:53,580 --> 00:41:57,249
会请你们喝一杯
to invite you in for a drink.

742
00:41:59,252 --> 00:42:01,419
或许我们该送他条狗
Maybe we should get him a dog?

743
00:42:01,453 --> 00:42:03,621
这个男人需要的可不只是一条狗
Ha! That man needs more than a dog.

744
00:42:03,656 --> 00:42:05,623
的确是
Yes, he does.

745
00:42:05,658 --> 00:42:08,393
我安排了护士每周给他做两次检查
I arranged for a nurse to check on him twice a week.

746
00:42:17,502 --> 00:42:19,670
嗨
Hey.

747
00:42:19,705 --> 00:42:21,672
嗨
Hey.

748
00:42:21,707 --> 00:42:24,141
真出乎意料啊
This is unexpected.

749
00:42:24,176 --> 00:42:26,343
但愿这不是不欢迎的意思
I hope that's not code for unwelcome.

750
00:42:26,377 --> 00:42:28,212
当然不是
Not at all.

751
00:42:28,246 --> 00:42:30,514
我在你家还落了别的东西吗
Did I leave something else at your place?

752
00:42:30,548 --> 00:42:32,515
事实上 我在想你的浴室里
Actually, I was wondering if there might be room

753
00:42:32,549 --> 00:42:35,551
是否装得下我的牙刷和沐浴露
in your bathroom for my toothbrush and body wash?

754
00:42:35,586 --> 00:42:39,022
我不太想来过夜时闻起来有一股麝香味儿
I kinda prefer not smelling like musky spice whenever I stay over.

755
00:42:39,056 --> 00:42:41,857
- 我喜欢 - 你会更爱这个的
- I like it. - You'll like this better.

756
00:42:44,127 --> 00:42:48,532
# 他们在我窗前翩翩起舞 #
They were dancing In my window 

757
00:42:48,533 --> 00:42:49,497
没错 我很喜欢
You're right, I do.

758
00:42:49,532 --> 00:42:53,235
# 你唤醒我对我说 #
You awoke to me and said

759
00:42:53,269 --> 00:42:55,803
# 这究竟意味着什么 #
You've been wondering what it meant

